// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0594 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 179b5818-aff1-5521-8ce4-5d9456cefce1

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
